git.message: 1.0.0 - fixes pipeline to find times recursively   - cleans up duplicate code - handles if git is not present - removes the dependency on having a package.json to get name and description - removes the qs module uses native querystring - cleans up stages markup to have the title inlined - adds report tab to show report in JSON - adds times to all pipeline nodes   - the end now shows a cumulative time - fixes bug if output is not defined in config - config is now the pipeline parsed - adds an output flag to the CLI that sets the output of the report - adds an browser flag to CLI that allows setting browser to be configured to be open or not - abstracts execution logic from binary and tests it separately - cleans up and rearranges UI - adds story to storybook stories to reflect a full report view - removes babel-minify-webpack-plugin
